      "level": 4,
      "text": "Productive Skills"
    },
    {
      "id": "n19",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 18,
      "text": "Official exam context"
    },
    {
      "id": "n20",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 19,
      "level": 2,
      "text": "What the Goethe A2 Exam Checks"
    },
    {
      "id": "n21",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 20,
      "text": "Goethe-Zertifikat A2 confirms basic German skills at the second CEFR level for adults."
    },
    {
      "id": "n22",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 21,
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Exam format and timing"
    },
    {
      "id": "n23",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 22,
      "text": "The exam has listening, reading, writing, and speaking sections. The speaking section is an oral pair exam."
    },
    {
      "id": "n24",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 23,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Listening"
    },
    {
      "id": "n25",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 24,
      "text": "30 minutes"
    },
    {
      "id": "n26",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 25,
      "text": "Everyday conversations, announcements, radio interviews, phone messages, and public announcements."
    },
    {
      "id": "n27",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 26,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Reading"
    },
    {
      "id": "n29",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 27,
      "text": "Short newspaper articles, emails, advertisements, and public information boards."
    },
    {
      "id": "n30",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 28,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Writing"
    },
    {
      "id": "n32",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 29,
      "text": "Messages related to your immediate living environment."
    },
    {
      "id": "n33",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 30,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Speaking"
    },
    {
      "id": "n34",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 31,
      "text": "15 minutes"
    },
    {
      "id": "n35",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 32,
      "text": "Questions about yourself, talking about your life, and planning something with a partner."
    },
    {
      "id": "n36",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 33,
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Best for"
    },
    {
      "id": "n37",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 34,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Everyday German checkpoint"
    },
    {
      "id": "n38",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 35,
      "text": "Good for learners who can handle simple routines and want proof beyond beginner level."
    },
    {
      "id": "n39",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 36,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Bridge to B1"
    },
    {
      "id": "n40",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 37,
      "text": "A2 is usually a stepping stone toward B1 for residence, citizenship, or more independent work and study goals."
    },
    {
      "id": "n41",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 38,
      "level": 3,
      "text": "How to use your practice time"
    },
    {
      "id": "n42",
      "type": "list",
      "order": 39,
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "Routine exchanges about background, education, immediate needs, and familiar topics."
        },
        {
          "text": "Short texts where you find essential information quickly."
        },
        {
          "text": "Speaking roleplay for asking, answering, planning, agreeing, and clarifying."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "n43",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 40,
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Frequently Asked Questions"
    },
    {
      "id": "n44",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 41,
      "text": "Everything you need to know about the exam!"
    },
    {
      "id": "n45",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 42,
      "text": "It proves basic German at CEFR A2 and is useful for course progression, everyday communication, and situations where A2 is specifically requested."
    },
    {
      "id": "n46",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 43,
      "text": "A2 expects more routine communication, longer everyday listening, short articles and emails, messages, and simple planning with another person."
    },
    {
      "id": "n47",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 44,
      "text": "Yes if your basics are shaky. A2 makes the jump to B1 writing and speaking much less painful."
    },
    {
      "id": "n48",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 45,
      "text": "Last reviewed: May 2026. This page is independent exam preparation. For official registration, fees, dates, and accepted certificate rules, check the exam provider and the institution or authority requesting your certificate."
    }
